description.excerpt: This repository build on the work of https://github.com/tkipf/gae, (N., Thomas, and Max. “Variational Graph Auto-Encoders.” ArXiv.org, 21 Nov. 2016, arxiv.org/abs/1611.07308.) to learn representations of scientific citation data into a latent space. If latent space is then a representation of the the underlying *information* in the dataset, investigating the latent space and their correlations with features, we can begin to understand how the features interact with each other in a complex networks - such as the scientific citation network.
This repository is built for the SoS Research at CCNR
